# What is this?
This is a website base to jumpscare your friends! Just customise the jumpscare and make a website from it using GitHub's pages feature!
# How do I jumpscare my friends
It's simple! Just follow these steps.
## Creating the repository
1. Click 'Use this template' > 'Create a new repository'
2. Fill in all the fields marked with a *. (name, owner, template, etc...)
3. Make the repository PUBLIC. Making it private won't allow you to use GitHub Pages
4. Create the repository
## Uploading the jumpscare
1. Go to the Sources folder
2. Upload a video (Note: Video must be named "Video.mp4" and have the .mp4 format)
## Making it a webpage
1. Click settings at the top
2. Click pages on the left
3. Under Branch click on 'None' and then 'main'
4. Click 'Save'
For more info check out this tutorial https://docs.github.com/en/pages/getting-started-with-github-pages/configuring-a-publishing-source-for-your-github-pages-site

Enjoy jumpscaring your friends!

